 this class, or to take a level in another class if you are already a bard.</p></blockquote><blockquote><h3>Bard Multiclassing Proficiencies</h3><p><strong>Proficiencies Gained:</strong> If bard is not your initial class, here are the proficiencies you gain when you take your first level as a bard: light armor, one musical instrument of your choice, one skill from the class's skill lists.</p></blockquote><blockquote><h3>Bard Multiclassing Spell Slots</h3><p><strong>Spell Slots</strong> Add your levels in the bard class to the appropriate levels from other classes to determine your available spell slots.</p></blockquote><p></p>",
